description: MidNord is bringing amazing empanadas to the streets of Minneapolis to satisfy your empanada cravings. You can try some of the more traditional options, or grab yourself one of MidNord's tasty innovations, such as the Mac Attack or the Buffalo Soldiers. They're stuffing dough on the streets of the Great Middle North, so come by and see what it's all about!
name: The MidNord Empanada Truck
